                                you'll find qualifications needed, salary,
                                prgression opportunities and a description of daily tasks involved.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="dfe-grid-container explore-dfe-grid-container">

                        <div class="dfe-card explore-dfe-card">
                            <div class="dfe-card-container explore-dfe-card-container">
                                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
                                    <a href="#" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state dfe-card-link--header">Card title</a>
                                </h3>
                                <p>A short description for the card.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="dfe-card explore-dfe-card">
                            <div class="dfe-card-container explore-dfe-card-container">
                                <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
                                    <a href="#" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-visited-state dfe-card-link--header">Card title</a>
                                </h3>
                                <p>A short description for the card.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                    
                                 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
            <div class="dfe-grid-container explore-dfe-grid-container-two">
                <h3><a class="class=" govuk-header__link" href="https://nationalcareers.service.gov.uk/skills-assessment">Take a skills assessment</a></h3>
                <p class="govuk-body">
                    If you're not sure where to start, answer questions
                    about your interest to find out which sectors may be best for you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
              
    </div>
</div>




